#: ../../source/manage_data/02.6. historypanel_visual.md:1
msgid "HistoryPanel 可视化"
msgstr "HistoryPanel Visualization"

#: ../../source/manage_data/02.6. historypanel_visual.md:3
#, python-format
msgid ""
"上一章 [HistoryPanel（历史数据面板）](2.5.%20historypanel.md) 介绍了如何把多"
"标的、多指标的历史数据对齐到同一块面板。本章说明如何**直接用面板出图**：与"
"「先 `to_share_frame` 再手写 matplotlib」相比，**`HistoryPanel.plot()`** 根"
"据当前 `htypes` 自动组合 K 线、成交量、MACD、折线等视图，使探索数据时的上下"
"文与策略研究阶段保持一致。"
msgstr ""
"The previous chapter, [HistoryPanel (Historical Data Panel)]"
"(2.5.%20historypanel.md), introduced how to align historical data from "
"multiple targets and indicators onto the same panel. This chapter explains "
"how to **directly plot data using the panel**: Compared to \"first using "
"`to_share_frame` and then manually writing matplotlib code\", "
"**`HistoryPanel.plot()`** automatically combines views such as candlestick "
"charts, volume, MACD, and line charts based on the current `htypes`, "
"ensuring consistency between the context of data exploration and the "
"strategy research phase."

#: ../../source/manage_data/02.6. historypanel_visual.md:7
msgid "`hp.plot()`：推荐的统一入口"
msgstr "`hp.plot()`: Recommended unified entry point"

#: ../../source/manage_data/02.6. historypanel_visual.md:9
msgid ""
"项目中将 **`HistoryPanel.plot()`** 作为**唯一推荐的制图入口**（旧有接口若仍"
"存在，语义上也应委托到同一套流水线）。你只需保证面板中非空且包含绘图所需的列"
"（例如完整 OHLC 才能出蜡烛图），其余图表类型由内部根据 `htypes` 自动判定。"
msgstr ""
"In this project, **`HistoryPanel.plot()`** is the **only recommended entry "
"point for plotting** (if the old interface still exists, it should also be "
"semantically delegated to the same pipeline). You only need to ensure that "
"the panel is not empty and contains the columns required for plotting "
"(e.g., a complete OHLC is required to generate a candlestick chart); other "
"chart types will be automatically determined internally based on `htypes`."

#: ../../source/manage_data/02.6. historypanel_visual.md:11
msgid ""
"常用参数含义如下（完整签名见 [HistoryPanel API](../api/HistoryPanel.rst)）："
msgstr ""
"The meanings of commonly used parameters are as follows (see [HistoryPanel "
"API](../api/HistoryPanel.rst) for the complete signature):"

#: ../../source/manage_data/02.6. historypanel_visual.md
msgid "参数"
msgstr "Parameters"

#: ../../source/manage_data/02.6. historypanel_visual.md
msgid "作用概要"
msgstr "Function Summary"

#: ../../source/manage_data/02.6. historypanel_visual.md
msgid "`shares`"
msgstr "`shares`"

#: ../../source/manage_data/02.6. historypanel_visual.md
msgid "要绘制的标的子集；默认使用面板内全部标的。"
msgstr ""
"A subset of the targets to be drawn; by default, all targets in the panel "
"are used."

#: ../../source/manage_data/02.6. historypanel_visual.md
msgid "`layout`"
msgstr "`layout`"

#: ../../source/manage_data/02.6. historypanel_visual.md
msgid ""
"多标的布局：`'overlay'`（同一坐标系叠加）、`'stack'`（分组纵向分面）、"
"`'auto'`（例如 2 只标的倾向 overlay，更多则 stack）。"
msgstr ""
"Multi-target layouts: \"overlay\" (overlaying within the same coordinate "
"system), \"stack\" (grouping and faceting vertically), \"auto\" (e.g., two "
"targets tend to be overlayed, more are stacked)."

#: ../../source/manage_data/02.6. historypanel_visual.md
msgid "`interactive`"
msgstr "`interactive`"

#: ../../source/manage_data/02.6. historypanel_visual.md
msgid ""
"`False` 使用 **matplotlib** 静态图；`True` 使用 **Plotly** 交互图（缩放、平"
"移、悬停等）。"
msgstr ""
"`False` uses a static plot from **matplotlib**; `True` uses an interactive "
"plot from **Plotly** (zoom, pan, hover, etc.)."

#: ../../source/manage_data/02.6. historypanel_visual.md
msgid "`highlight`"
msgstr "`highlight`"

#: ../../source/manage_data/02.6. historypanel_visual.md
msgid "高亮极值点等，例如 `'max'` / `'min'` 或传入配置字典。"
msgstr ""
"Highlight extreme values, such as 'max' / 'min', or pass in a configuration "
"dictionary."

#: ../../source/manage_data/02.6. historypanel_visual.md
msgid "`plotly_backend_app`"
msgstr "`plotly_backend_app`"

#: ../../source/manage_data/02.6. historypanel_visual.md
msgid ""
"仅在 `interactive=True` 时有效：`'auto'`（优先 FigureWidget，失败则回退 "
"HTML 包装）、`'FigureWidget'`、`'html'`。"
msgstr ""
"Only valid when `interactive=True`: `'auto'` (prefers FigureWidget, falls "
"back to HTML wrapper if it fails), `'FigureWidget'`, `'html'`."

#: ../../source/manage_data/02.6. historypanel_visual.md:21
msgid ""
"**说明**：当请求的标的数量较多时，实现可能会**限制实际绘制的标的数量**并发出"
"警告，以避免单图过载；具体以当前版本行为为准。多标的布局的细微调整与历史修复"
"说明见 [RELEASE_HISTORY](../RELEASE_HISTORY.md) 中 2.2.x 相关条目。"
msgstr ""
"**Note:** When the number of requested targets is large, the implementation "
"may **limit the number of targets actually drawn** and issue a warning to "
"avoid overloading a single graph; the specific behavior is subject to the "
"current version. For details on minor adjustments to the layout of multiple "
"targets and historical fixes, please refer to the relevant entries in "
"[RELEASE_HISTORY](../RELEASE_HISTORY.md) 2.2.x."

#: ../../source/manage_data/02.6. historypanel_visual.md:23
msgid "静态图与交互图"
msgstr "Static diagrams and interactive diagrams"

#: ../../source/manage_data/02.6. historypanel_visual.md:25
msgid ""
"**`interactive=False`（默认）**：依赖 **matplotlib**，适合脚本批量出图、生成"
"静态文件；不强制安装 Plotly。"
msgstr ""
"**`interactive=False` (default): Depends on **matplotlib**, suitable for "
"batch plotting and generating static files using scripts; does not force "
"the installation of Plotly."

#: ../../source/manage_data/02.6. historypanel_visual.md:26
msgid ""
"**`interactive=True`**：依赖 **plotly**；在 Jupyter 中若 **`anywidget` 与 "
"`ipywidgets`** 可用，通常可得到 **FigureWidget**，表头与坐标轴交互更完整；否"
"则可能回退为 **HTML 包装** 形式，仍具备基本交互，但与 Widget 路径在体验上略"
"有差异。"
msgstr ""
"**interactive=True**: Depends on **plotly**; in Jupyter, if **anywidget** "
"and **ipywidgets** are available, you can usually get a **FigureWidget**, "
"which has more complete interaction between the header and axes; otherwise, "
"it may fall back to the **HTML wrapper** form, which still has basic "
"interaction, but the experience is slightly different from the Widget path."

#: ../../source/manage_data/02.6. historypanel_visual.md:28
msgid "极简示例（需本地已有 OHLCV 或等价列；仅作形式演示）："
msgstr ""
"Minimalist example (requires existing OHLCV or equivalent columns locally; "
"for demonstration purposes only):"

#: ../../source/manage_data/02.6. historypanel_visual.md:43
msgid ""
"当主图为蜡烛图时，静态图会在时间轴**最后一根 K 线**上显示 OHLC 摘要；交互图"
"默认一致，点击某根 K 线后摘要会更新为该根（面向用户的摘要文案为英文）。无完"
"整 OHLC 时不会出现该摘要区。"
msgstr ""
"When the main chart is a candlestick chart, the static chart will display "
"an OHLC summary on the **last candlestick** on the timeline; the "
"interactive chart is consistent by default, and clicking on a candlestick "
"will update the summary to that candlestick (the summary text for the user "
"is in English). This summary area will not appear if there is no complete "
"OHLC."

#: ../../source/manage_data/02.6. historypanel_visual.md:45
msgid "布局与多标的"
msgstr "Layout and multiple targets"

#: ../../source/manage_data/02.6. historypanel_visual.md:47
msgid ""
"**`overlay`**：适合对比少数标的（如两只股票）在同一价格尺度下的走势（具体是"
"否共享 y 轴以当前实现为准）。"
msgstr ""
"**overlay:** Suitable for comparing the price movements of a few targets "
"(such as two stocks) at the same price scale (whether they share the y-axis "
"depends on the current implementation)."

#: ../../source/manage_data/02.6. historypanel_visual.md:48
msgid ""
"**`stack`**：每个标的（或每组）单独占一行子图，适合标的较多、避免挤在同一坐"
"标系。"
msgstr ""
"**`stack`: Each target (or group) occupies a separate sub-plot, suitable "
"for a large number of targets and to avoid them being crammed into the same "
"coordinate system."

#: ../../source/manage_data/02.6. historypanel_visual.md:49
msgid "**`auto`**：在标的数量较少时倾向叠加，较多时倾向分面，减少手动试错。"
msgstr ""
"**auto:** When the number of targets is small, it tends to stack them; when "
"the number is large, it tends to split them into facets, reducing manual "
"trial and error."

#: ../../source/manage_data/02.6. historypanel_visual.md:51
msgid ""
"若某版本后布局语义有调整，**以对应版本的 [RELEASE_HISTORY](../"
"RELEASE_HISTORY.md) 说明为准**。"
msgstr ""
"If the layout semantics are adjusted in a later version, **the description "
"in the corresponding version's [RELEASE_HISTORY](../RELEASE_HISTORY.md) "
"shall prevail.**"

#: ../../source/manage_data/02.6. historypanel_visual.md:53
msgid "依赖与安装提示"
msgstr "Dependency and Installation Tips"

#: ../../source/manage_data/02.6. historypanel_visual.md:55
msgid "**静态图**：一般需要 **matplotlib**（与 qteasy 常用环境一致）。"
msgstr ""
"**Static plots:** generally require **matplotlib** (the same environment "
"commonly used with qteasy)."

#: ../../source/manage_data/02.6. historypanel_visual.md:56
msgid ""
"**交互图**：需要 **plotly**；完整 Notebook 交互体验建议同时安装 "
"**ipywidgets** 与 **anywidget**。可选依赖的版本范围以项目 "
"**`pyproject.toml`** 或安装文档为准，本文不逐条罗列版本号。"
msgstr ""
"**Interactive Graphs**: Requires **plotly**; for a complete Notebook "
"interactive experience, it is recommended to install both **ipywidgets** "
"and **anywidget**. The version range of optional dependencies is based on "
"the project's **`pyproject.toml`** or the installation documentation; this "
"document does not list version numbers individually."

#: ../../source/manage_data/02.6. historypanel_visual.md:58
msgid ""
"底层渲染模块名与扩展点仅供开发者阅读源码时使用；用户文档不展开文件级实现细"
"节。"
msgstr ""
"The underlying rendering module name and extension point are only for "
"developers to use when reading the source code; the user documentation does "
"not elaborate on the file-level implementation details."

#: ../../source/manage_data/02.6. historypanel_visual.md:60
msgid "小结"
msgstr "summary"

#: ../../source/manage_data/02.6. historypanel_visual.md:62
#, python-format
msgid ""
"数据准备仍通过 **`get_history_data`** 等与 [上一章](2.5.%20historypanel.md) "
"一致；制图统一走 **`hp.plot()`**。"
msgstr ""
"Data preparation is still done using **`get_history_data`**, consistent "
"with [Previous Chapter](2.5.%20historypanel.md); plotting is done using "
"**`hp.plot()`**."

#: ../../source/manage_data/02.6. historypanel_visual.md:63
msgid ""
"**`interactive`** 与 **`layout`** 是日常最常被改动的两个开关；进阶参数见 "
"API 文档。"
msgstr ""
"**`interactive`** and **`layout`** are the two switches that are most "
"frequently modified in daily use; see the API documentation for advanced "
"parameters."

#: ../../source/manage_data/02.6. historypanel_visual.md:64
msgid ""
"行为变更与可视化相关修复请查阅 **[RELEASE_HISTORY](../"
"RELEASE_HISTORY.md)**；动手练习可配合教程 **[使用 HistoryPanel 操作和分析历"
"史数据](../tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md)**。"
msgstr ""
"For behavior changes and visualization-related fixes, please refer to "
"**[RELEASE_HISTORY](../RELEASE_HISTORY.md)**; for hands-on exercises, "
"please refer to the tutorial **[Using HistoryPanel to Manipulate and "
"Analyze Historical Data](../tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md)**."
